### SHIPPER API TESTS

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001/api/v1
@shipperEmail = shipper1@foodapp.com
@password = password123

# @name loginShipper
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identifier": "{{shipperEmail}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###
@shipperToken = {{loginShipper.response.body.data.accessToken}}
@orderId = YOUR_ORDER_ID_HERE

### 1. Get Shipper's Delivery Schedule
# Status: READY
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/kitchen/delivery-schedule
Authorization: Bearer {{shipperToken}}

### 2. Confirm Pickup
# Status: READY -> DELIVERING
# Delivery Status: PENDING/SHIPPER_ASSIGNED -> PICKED_UP
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/internal/orders/{{orderId}}/pickup
Authorization: Bearer {{shipperToken}}

### 3. Complete Delivery
# Status: DELIVERING -> COMPLETED
# Delivery Status: PICKED_UP -> DELIVERED
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/internal/orders/{{orderId}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{shipperToken}}
